全美拒绝者因节日“管理变更”退出《当我们年轻时》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-all-american-rejects-pull-out-of-when-we-were-young-following-festival-management-change-3802096?utm_source=rss&utm_medium= rss&utm_campaign=全美国人拒绝退出当我们年轻时跟随节日管理变化Laura MolloySat, 12 Oct 2024 08:59:01 +0000 Music NewsNewsEmoLive Music NewsPop-Punk https://www.nme.com/?p=3802096 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Tyson-Ritter-of-the-All-American-Rejects.-CREDIT_-Matt-Winkelmeyer_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Tyson-Ritter-of-the-All-American-Rejects.-CREDIT_-Matt-Winkelmeyer_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Tyson-Ritter-of-the-All-American-Rejects.-CREDIT_-Matt-Winkelmeyer_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Tyson-Ritter-of-the-All-American-Rejects.-CREDIT_-Matt-Winkelmeyer_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Tyson-Ritter-of-the-All-American-Rejects.-CREDIT_-Matt-Winkelmeyer_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Tyson-Ritter-of-the-All-American-Rejects.-CREDIT_-Matt-Winkelmeyer_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Tyson-Ritter-of-the-All-American-Rejects.-CREDIT_-Matt-Winkelmeyer_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> emo 音乐节将于 10 月 19 日至 20 日在拉斯维加斯举行</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-all-american-rejects-pull-out-of-when-we-were-young-following-festival-management-change-3802096">因音乐节“管理层变更”，全美拒绝者退出《当我们年轻时》的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Tyson-Ritter-of-the-All-American-Rejects.-CREDIT_-Matt-Winkelmeyer_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Tyson-Ritter-of-the-All-American-Rejects.-CREDIT_-Matt-Winkelmeyer_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Tyson-Ritter-of-the-All-American-Rejects.-CREDIT_-Matt-Winkelmeyer_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Tyson-Ritter-of-the-All-American-Rejects.-CREDIT_-Matt-Winkelmeyer_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Tyson-Ritter-of-the-All-American-Rejects.-CREDIT_-Matt-Winkelmeyer_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Tyson-Ritter-of-the-All-American-Rejects.-CREDIT_-Matt-Winkelmeyer_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Tyson-Ritter-of-the-All-American-Rejects.-CREDIT_-Matt-Winkelmeyer_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>全美拒绝者乐队宣布，他们将不再参加<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/when-we-were-young">《当我们年轻时》的</a>演出，因为音乐节的管理人员“无法容纳”他们。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/how-when-we-were-young-went-from-emo-fyre-fest-to-a-euphoric-pop-punk-party-3336793">《当我们年轻时》如何从“情绪狂欢节”转变为欢快的流行朋克派对</a></strong></li></ul><p>2024 年拉斯维加斯 emo bash 将于 10 月 19 日至 20 日举行。他们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/my-chemical-romance-fall-out-boy-jimmy-eat-world-and-more-to-play-classic-albums-in-full-at-when-we-were-young-2024-3537815">去年公布了阵容</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/my-chemical-romance">《My Chemical Romance》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fall-out-boy">《Fall Out Boy</a> 》和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jimmy-eat-world">《Jimmy Eat World》</a>将完整演奏他们的经典专辑。</p><p>但现在，全美拒绝者队已经退出。乐队原定于 2002 年演奏他们的首张同名专辑，但他们表示，在音乐节“管理层变动”后，他们将不再演奏。</p><p>在分享给 Instagram 的一份声明中，他们写道：“我们花了几个月的时间不知疲倦地准备一场千载难逢的演出，我们很高兴能为大家带来这场演出。然而，WWWY 的管理层发生了变动，他们无法再将我们安置在之前商定的阵容中，这让我们无法继续下去。”</p><p>他们接着说：“我们感到特别沮丧，因为你们无法为那些穿越手套来见证我们在大锅中酝酿的视觉和声音奇观的人打球。我们要向我们出色的工作人员道歉，他们夜以继日地工作，让奇迹发生。”</p><p> <em>《NME》</em>已联系《当我们年轻时》发表评论。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DA_XhLePeh2/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.24